" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/4d2dfed3e4dc94b0c9c75de6512cad69.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carnal Contract 是一款視覺小說遊戲，它爲您提供了多種不同的元素——一個充滿懸念的引人入勝的故事，通過選擇影響主角愛情生活的可能性，當然，還有大量的欲望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中也充滿了與許多精心設計的女性的性感機會和行動。您將很難決定要追求哪一個。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d91eb8e2a6da88ea8ee98095abf5616.poster.avif?t=1770909148\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d91eb8e2a6da88ea8ee98095abf5616.webm?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d91eb8e2a6da88ea8ee98095abf5616.mp4?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/89c1f7a7a282b53e822c75a67d49e6ae.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爲了確保非凡的遊戲體驗，尤其是在那些性感時刻，遊戲設計了多種動畫，爲角色注入了生命。這些動畫提升了您的遊戲體驗，讓您更深入地沉浸在遊戲世界中。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/94d5437b3c185839a2248c730ebafa2e.poster.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/94d5437b3c185839a2248c730ebafa2e.webm?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/94d5437b3c185839a2248c730ebafa2e.mp4?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/ddf66fa125743ff418dae8bbd9a6b45d.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哦，我們提到您住在一個有三個漂亮女人的房子裡了嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沒有？那麼，您將發現自己與她們處於許多情境中，在那裡您可以感受到緊張，甚至可能墜入愛河。遊戲旅程將讓您面臨各種場景，激起您的道德指南和欲望之間的衝突。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些時刻可能看似無法逾越的障礙，但總有機會把事情做對。您與家中女性的互動將根據您的選擇而演變。您認爲自己可以誘惑她們三個嗎？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/7ed972ca7a51831762c43b1b23ed283d.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/7d4414c21e4f61640f198160bb857db6.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的每一個決定都將鋪設一條通向不同結局的獨特道路。某些選擇對於特定的戀愛對象而言具有更大的分量，可能會讓您離她們更近或更遠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有時，您會意識到自己無法擁有一切，這種覺悟可能只會在您接近遊戲結局時才會浮現。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d40084ecd5740eab3ad4389cedcc4fc.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/1b364f8b8e0d72d6cbc46bbae709862f.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一個獨特的遊戲特色是「性感模式」，它可以轉換某些渲染圖，提供另一種視角。想象一下戴着一副特殊的眼鏡；切換這個模式會神奇地改變渲染圖中女孩們的服裝，或者讓她們完全裸體——很調皮，是吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/ea40a2a52ba3a5f477b20918ad153fa1.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/17965a99f27ed01076a7fca223a58a84.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/4dfd6d0fea9a85599be5015cf07e97e6.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/d1b41635d4dd91bbd8f1588d8e6b5f85.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲包含：裸露、暗示性暴力、酒精和藥物使用描寫、口交、陰道性交、肛交和非插入性性行爲的露骨描繪以及常見BDSM場景。</p>", "short_description": "Carnal Contract 是一部成人視覺小說，您將扮演一個身陷巨額債務的年輕人。一個奇怪的遊戲提供了擺脫困境的方法，但前提是他敢於完成情慾挑戰。遊戲充滿了性愛、懸念、各種挑戰和戲劇性。", "supported_languages": "英文, 法文, 簡體中文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 西班牙文 - 拉丁美洲, 繁體中文, 俄文, 土耳其文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/325823f22b23db3ec44303860748efd41f41fe14/header.jpg?t=1770909148", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/ecfbdd1096c1ec728b81e508c70c1fdb7c453345/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1770909148", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/ecfbdd1096c1ec728b81e508c70c1fdb7c453345/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1770909148", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows XP or higher<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 GHz Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 2.0 or DirectX 9.0c compatible<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> OS X Yosemite 10.10<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 2, DirectX 9, OpenGL ES 2 or WebGL<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Ubuntu 12.04+ or Kernel 3.x+ based distributions<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 GHz Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["Dotty Diaries"], "publishers": ["Dotty Diaries"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 26800, "final": 26800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 268"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}, {"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 8 月 27 日"}}}}, "us": {"2484170": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Carnal Contract", "steam_appid": 2484170, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3942200], "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/e3dd2e9da50e0d0a631abadf05e58d30.avif?t=1770909148\" width=616 height=212 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What was supposed to be a simple summer break takes an unexpected twist when you find yourself trapped in a strange game where you need to fulfill challenges. Carnal challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/e5ad043241a949223b3462ffd9d1b01b.poster.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/e5ad043241a949223b3462ffd9d1b01b.webm?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/e5ad043241a949223b3462ffd9d1b01b.mp4?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/bff15d3c9a673cfef1681cbe76b0ae15.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing as the main character, you will quickly feel the game's unsettling influence on your closest relationships, and how it is slowly, but surely, trying to corrupt your mind.  Will you give in to your desires? Where does the game come from? What is its origin and motive? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You yearn to discover its secrets, but the constant sensation of being watched only adds to the intrigue. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/baaba19be12e7055ae7ef6e141df00d2.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/85be55bbea438eb95119b78f42273e9a.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span>The narrative purposefully  places  you in challenging situations that force a deeper introspection into your motives. As the creator of your destiny, you encounter someone manipulating you into dangerous challenges for their own entertainment. With a loved one drawn into the fray, your moral compass clashes with your lust, muddling your choices.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you understand that the danger might be even closer than you thought, an unexpected heroic role comes up—will you rise to the occasion and save her in time? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/9e18f53ca9bcbac65bd1d30332f6293f.poster.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/9e18f53ca9bcbac65bd1d30332f6293f.webm?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/9e18f53ca9bcbac65bd1d30332f6293f.mp4?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/8a6ca96a16ef00863b391ae0311a1ca3.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span>Every episode introduces a fresh challenge, allowing you the choice to tackle the first two. However, the subsequent challenges are non-negotiable. Your decisions are yours to make, but the consequences of not completing them remain a mystery. Prepare for a multitude of choices leading you toward diverse events and scenes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may not see some scenes if certain prerequisites aren't met. Proceeding without exploring all possibilities means missing out on potential adventures with the ladies. Are you willing to risk that and possibly miss out on the action? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/d11de8ff0b0f50fde1b4935b800f8113.avif?t=1770909148\" width=604 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/42cfbd00db80598eacfa4a55a747d293.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span>There will be plenty of moments in which you will have to take action. Sometimes, you will not be able to do it all, so you will have to make a decision. Be mindful, as your actions wield consequences that can unlock or lock specific content in future episodes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/a115224179cf8b55299c179878f8fe07.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/3a50c0dcc1311747e2368bf79cc9243f.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span>Carnal Contract is a visual novel game that offers you a plethora of different elements - an engaging story shrouded with mystery, the possibility to influence the MC’s love life through choices and, of course, plenty of lust.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s also full of sexy opportunities and action with many girls designed with attention to detail. It will be hard to decide which one you want to pursue.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d91eb8e2a6da88ea8ee98095abf5616.poster.avif?t=1770909148\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d91eb8e2a6da88ea8ee98095abf5616.webm?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d91eb8e2a6da88ea8ee98095abf5616.mp4?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/4dc4c42a7ae21fb1e540a3144da1a85c.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To ensure an exceptional gaming experience, especially during those sexy moments, the game is designed with multiple animations that breathe life into the characters. These animations elevate your gameplay, giving you a deeper immersion within the game's world.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/94d5437b3c185839a2248c730ebafa2e.poster.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/94d5437b3c185839a2248c730ebafa2e.webm?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/94d5437b3c185839a2248c730ebafa2e.mp4?t=1770909148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/5469389b975d5f7c537672e22fcfee62.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span>Oh, and did we mention that you live in a house with three beautiful women? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No? Well, you will find yourself in many situations with them where you can feel the tension and maybe even fall in love. The game's journey will confront you with diverse scenarios, stirring a conflict between your moral compass and desires.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some moments may seem like impassable hurdles, yet there's always a chance to make it right. Your interactions with the women in your household will evolve based on your choices. Do you think you can seduce all three of them? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/7ed972ca7a51831762c43b1b23ed283d.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/aadbb62f088344067776a92e3b46509d.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600 height=148 /></span>Each decision you make paves a unique path toward distinct endings. Certain choices hold more weight in relation to a particular love interest, potentially pulling you closer or further from them.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At times, you'll realize you can't have everything, a realization that may only surface as you approach the conclusion of the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484170/extras/0d40084ecd5740eab3ad4389cedcc4fc.avif?t=1770909148\" width=600